This file marks that the project's wiki/ follows the Diátaxis four-mode
convention from ADR 0004 of agentic-harness:

  tutorials/   — learning-oriented, numbered-step walkthroughs
  how-to/      — task-oriented recipes
  reference/   — canonical lookup tables, flags, APIs
  explanation/ — narrative rationale, intent, ADRs

Presence of this marker enables strict-mode `check-wiki.py` for this
project. Do not remove unless you are migrating away from Diátaxis.

See:
- wiki/README.md — the convention as it applies here.
- https://github.com/alexherrero/agentic-harness/blob/main/wiki/architecture/decisions/0004-diataxis-documentation-spec.md
